text: Ryan Kwanten (born 28 November 1976) is an Australian actor. He played Vinnie Patterson from 1997 to 2002 in the Australian soap opera Home and Away. After his stint ended he joined the American teen drama series Summerland, portraying Jay Robertson. In 2008, he was cast as Jason Stackhouse in True Blood, he roles the animated voice talents in Legend of the Guardians: The Owls of Ga'Hoole and Blinky Bill the Movie. ==Other websites== * Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian voice actors Category:1976 births Category:Living people
